{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_10_01",
  "title": "白石沙季 1話 恋愛についての勉強",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ\nお疲れ様です、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Phew.\nGood work‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、沙季\n今日のライブも大盛り上がりだったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ Saki.\nToday’s live was a huge success too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ファン参加型の歌唱ライブでしたから\n一体感があって、私も楽しかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since it was a fan-participation singing live‚\nit had a sense of unity‚ and I really enjoyed it too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "余韻に浸りたいところではありますが\n明日の仕事のためにも今日は早めに上がらないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d like to savor the afterglow‚ but—\nI need to wrap up early for tomorrow’s work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "明日は月ストのみんな別々の仕事ですよね\n琴乃ちゃんはラジオで、すずちゃんは雑誌の撮影で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomorrow everyone in Moon Tempest has different jobs‚ right?\nKotono-chan has radio‚ Suzu-chan has a magazine shoot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.5000020345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さすがは沙季だな。みんなのスケジュールも\n頭に入っているだなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of Saki. You’ve even memorized\neveryone’s schedule too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9565437064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "みんながどんな仕事をしているのかを\n把握しておくのは大事ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s important to know what work\neveryone is doing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.6666687012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "本当は休ませてあげたいんだが\nBIG4になってからますます注目されていてな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really do want to let you rest‚\nbut ever since you became BIG4‚ the attention has only grown…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "心配しないで下さい、まだまだ平気です\nむしろもっと頑張れますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry. I’m still perfectly fine.\nIf anything‚ I can work even harder.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.833334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.533334605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、こうして仕事をこなしていくことで\n私達が活躍する姿をファンに届けることが出来ます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And by steadily doing this work‚\nwe can show our fans us at our best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3000012716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "恵まれている今だからこそ\n体力の許す限り頑張らないと……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because we’re blessed right now‚\nI have to push myself as much as my stamina allows…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.0000012716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.7666679383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。だが、疲れを感じ始めたら\nすぐに言ってほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. But if you start feeling tired‚\nplease tell me right away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4000012716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーとして、沙季が倒れるような事態は\n絶対に避けなくちゃいけないからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As your manager‚ letting you collapse is something\nI absolutely must avoid.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.551181119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.0999997457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "肝に銘じておきます\n体調管理もアイドルとしての大切な役目ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll keep that firmly in mind.\nManaging my health is an important duty as an idol too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.7999997457
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.5041347184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（平静を装っているが、さすがに疲れが見えるな）\n（俺の方でどうにかしてあげられたらいいんだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She’s trying to look calm‚ but I can see she’s tired.）\n（If only there were something I could do for her…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.5041347184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.5000043233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.5000043114
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.5000043114
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "ロケのお仕事、ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A location shoot job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.3666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。番組のプロデューサーから\n沙季に出演してほしいと直々に指名があったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. The show’s producer\nspecifically requested you to appear.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.5999997457,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8000,
          "startTime": 112.5999997457
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.5999997457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "昼からの仕事だが、日帰りになる予定だな\nこれが資料だ、確認してみてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a job starting in the afternoon‚ but it should be a day trip.\nHere’s the material—take a look.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.5999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "……この番組は観たことがあります\nテーマ毎にいろいろな街を取り上げる番組でしたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’ve seen this show before.\nIt’s the one that covers different towns by theme‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.3333351135
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "月ストではなく、私一人に指名がきたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And they requested me alone‚ not Moon Tempest as a group?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.3333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "今回の番組のテーマが歴史関係らしくてな\n知的なイメージの沙季にぴったりだと思ったらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seems this time’s theme is history-related.\nThey thought your intellectual image would be perfect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.5666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.8666684468
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。それにしても、ロケの仕事は久しぶりです\n撮影やライブ続きでしたので気分転換になりそうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. By the way‚ it’s been a while since I’ve done a location shoot.\nWith all the shoots and lives lately‚ this might be a nice change of pace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.4666664124,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4700.0015259000065,
          "startTime": 145.1666679383
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.1666679383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "ふむふむ……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ hmm… huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.000004832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "何か気になることでもあったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something catch your attention?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.3333381653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
